    "en": {
      "title": "China's foreign trade up 9.4 percent",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In the first half of 2022, China's total imports and exports rose 9.4% year-on-year.",
        "Accordingly, China's total import and export value expanded to 19.8 trillion yuan (US$2.94 trillion), the data added."
      ],
